<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-66-0270 </DOCNO><TEXT>This patent describes a light transmitter comprising a cleaved-coupledcavity laser comprising a laser section and a modulator section, meansfor measuring at least one characteristic of the light output from oneof the sections with respect to the current through the modulator section;and feedback means using at least one characteristic to maintain theoutput at a desired spectral value.</TEXT></DOC>